markdownRemark.html:
Having grown up on the east coast, I often find myself longing for the warm summer evenings, crisp winter air, and distinct nature and foliage. I loved peering into my backyard with the dappled sunlight illuminating through tall maple trees on a summer afternoon.

This collection features scenes from New York City, Massachusetts, Maine, and New Hampshire during the summer and fall seasons.
